{
  "stem": "9898.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] May 30, 1949, I came to the United States, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the blessed country.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know a word of English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to make a telephone call, and I took the money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I asked them, what is the dime, and what is a nickel?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was a dime, the telephone call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She knew English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to, to a-- not to a residency, but I became a-- see, you forget?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Before the residency.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Internship.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Internship in a hospital, Coney Island Hospital in Brooklyn, New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there for one year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was difficult for me because I didn't know any English, and I had to write histories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my wife helped me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But after three months, I knew English because there was a-- an American boy who studied in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, there is only one way you can learn English-- is watch the television but only-- no singing, but the cowboy shows where they talk.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how I learned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it wasn't that easy there, but I was already-- I mean, I have the-- we had the rotating internship.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was three months in obstetrics.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for me, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, the, the, the chief of obstetrics, she left me alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was delivering the kids, tens of them because she was trusting me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I told you my history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was in summer of 1950.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a general-- a general, retired general from Pennsylvania came to our hospital and tried to get a few physician to work in a tuberculosis hospital in Pennsylvania, in South Mountain near Gettysburg.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So naturally, I went, and I told him my experiences.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he heard this, boy, he grabbed me immediately.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
